description: A collection of circles in a semi-circular formation with a line of circles wrapping around it; there are also two semi-circular formations extending downwards from the bottom of the larger one with two triangular formations below them. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a black triangle on the right side of the large semi-circular formation and a brown triangle in the center of the two conjoined semi-circular formations.
